WEBVTT

01:40.000 --> 01:42.720
Demons may not stir up trouble,
but humans can.

01:47.920 --> 01:48.760
Luo Wei,

01:49.520 --> 01:50.560
you're worse than a demon.

01:52.000 --> 01:54.320
One, two, three, four.

01:54.400 --> 01:55.800
These four things

01:55.880 --> 01:59.480
are the keys
to tonight's fox demon murder case.

02:00.440 --> 02:01.760
Ji, you're amazing!

02:01.840 --> 02:03.520
Stop keeping us in suspense. Spill it.

02:04.720 --> 02:05.840
After Wei Qing died,

02:05.920 --> 02:09.080
it's obvious Ms. Yu planned
to leave immediately.

02:09.160 --> 02:12.440
In the bags she packed,
besides her own clothes,

02:13.240 --> 02:14.480
there were also Steward Luo's.

02:15.040 --> 02:19.560
So, Ms. Yu was planning
to run away with you, right?

02:21.680 --> 02:24.120
But Yu Shengwei
is from a respectable family.

02:24.200 --> 02:25.560
If she suddenly vanished,

02:25.640 --> 02:28.680
the Yus would report it
and search the entire city.

02:28.760 --> 02:33.360
So how could she
completely escape this place?

02:34.480 --> 02:36.280
I know you don't love him.

02:37.000 --> 02:38.960
If it weren't for that talisman,

02:39.480 --> 02:41.080
you'd never have married him.

02:44.960 --> 02:47.920
I don't want to be trapped
in this mansion for life.

02:53.560 --> 02:56.120
Wherever you go, I'll follow.

02:57.600 --> 02:59.040
But if you disappear,

03:00.320 --> 03:04.280
your family and the authorities
will come looking.

03:08.760 --> 03:09.880
I have a plan.

03:11.480 --> 03:13.440
To vanish completely,

03:14.520 --> 03:15.840
you must first die.

03:15.920 --> 03:18.560
Fake your death to get away.
Nice and clean.

03:19.080 --> 03:20.240
That's a really good plan.

03:20.320 --> 03:21.160
Smart.

03:21.720 --> 03:23.520
But Ms. Yu is even smarter.

03:23.600 --> 03:26.440
She perfectly used
the fox demon chaos in the mansion

03:26.520 --> 03:29.560
to make everyone believe
she died at its claws.

03:45.040 --> 03:48.800
So, the fox demon shadow
we saw outside her room?

04:06.720 --> 04:10.320
They planned to use shadow play
to lure us away,

04:10.400 --> 04:12.400
<i>sending everyone after the fox demon.</i>

04:16.200 --> 04:19.839
<i>That way, they could</i>
<i>sneak away without a trace.</i>

04:19.920 --> 04:22.840
When we returned and found no body,
we'd be helpless,

04:22.920 --> 04:26.160
only able to assume the fox demon took her
or ate her.

04:28.200 --> 04:31.320
Pulling a stunt right under our noses,

04:32.040 --> 04:33.360
two fox demons?

04:34.720 --> 04:35.720
Trying to teach a master?

04:37.480 --> 04:38.720
No.

04:38.800 --> 04:40.760
Trying to fool Li Jie!

04:40.840 --> 04:41.720
Thanks.

04:41.800 --> 04:42.960
You're welcome.

04:45.640 --> 04:47.120
Sit up straight.

04:47.200 --> 04:48.240
Look at you.

04:50.760 --> 04:52.000
So mean!

04:52.080 --> 04:52.960
And you.

05:08.840 --> 05:09.920
Anything else?

05:10.680 --> 05:12.440
Yes!

05:13.360 --> 05:14.360
Next,

05:14.440 --> 05:17.760
how did they manage to lure the people
away from the front courtyard?

05:17.840 --> 05:21.720
Do you remember
that Ms. Yu is best at embroidering?

05:21.800 --> 05:24.040
She's Luo'an's famous embroiderer,

05:24.560 --> 05:27.280
especially skilled at stitching
birds and beasts.

05:27.360 --> 05:28.640
Birds and beasts.

05:28.720 --> 05:29.800
Exactly.

05:30.400 --> 05:31.240
Here.

05:45.960 --> 05:48.600
<i>Before everyone gathered</i>
<i>in the front yard for the ceremony,</i>

05:48.680 --> 05:51.880
<i>Steward Luo had already hung up</i>
<i>this cloth with a fox there.</i>

05:57.480 --> 05:59.760
<i>Then, she just needed</i>
<i>to lure everyone over</i>

05:59.840 --> 06:01.720
<i>to see the fox demon with their own eyes.</i>

06:01.800 --> 06:03.200
A fox demon…

06:04.040 --> 06:04.880
It's a fox demon!

06:13.440 --> 06:15.120
But when we got to the dye workshop,

06:15.200 --> 06:17.360
we didn't see that cloth.

06:17.880 --> 06:19.720
Unlike a man's feelings,

06:19.800 --> 06:23.600
it couldn't just disappear
in the blink of an eye.

06:25.000 --> 06:27.720
Not every man's feelings
disappear in a blink.

06:29.200 --> 06:30.040
Really?

06:32.000 --> 06:35.200
This piece here is the black cloth
with the fox Ms. Yu embroidered.

06:38.480 --> 06:39.320
Where's the fox?

06:40.400 --> 06:42.360
This is Steward Luo's smartest move.

06:42.880 --> 06:45.360
She really did make the fox
disappear in a blink.

06:47.280 --> 06:48.800
So, Steward Luo can use demon magic?

06:49.560 --> 06:50.480
Nothing to do with magic.

06:51.160 --> 06:52.120
It's the kite.

06:54.240 --> 06:55.880
What a huge kite!

06:58.120 --> 06:59.440
<i>Back in my hometown,</i>

06:59.960 --> 07:01.800
<i>they say when bad things happen,</i>

07:01.880 --> 07:03.560
<i>we should buy a kite and fly it away.</i>

07:04.280 --> 07:05.800
<i>The higher the kite flies,</i>

07:05.880 --> 07:08.000
<i>the further the bad luck goes.</i>

07:29.560 --> 07:33.240
<i>The kite flew away with threads</i>
<i>from the embroidery.</i>

07:33.320 --> 07:35.440
<i>The silver threads</i>
<i>were pulled out bit by bit.</i>

07:35.960 --> 07:38.320
<i>So the fox demon naturally vanished.</i>

07:38.400 --> 07:39.680
Indeed.

07:39.760 --> 07:42.720
This cloth is covered in needle holes.

07:53.760 --> 07:54.840
Interesting.

07:57.480 --> 08:00.680
Two mortals went to great lengths
to set up a fake fox demon,

08:01.240 --> 08:03.920
never expecting the real one to show up.

08:05.160 --> 08:06.120
Xiaowei,

08:07.680 --> 08:08.920
were you helping them?

08:09.760 --> 08:11.560
I just wanted to hold you off…

08:13.640 --> 08:15.240
to buy Shengwei some time.

08:16.360 --> 08:18.920
But in the end, you only hurt her.

08:21.440 --> 08:22.880
People with evil hearts

08:23.400 --> 08:26.160
are scarier than demons.

08:26.680 --> 08:27.560
You…

08:29.240 --> 08:30.600
Don't you dare slander me!

08:30.680 --> 08:33.120
A fox demon killed Ms. Yu
and ripped out her heart!

08:33.760 --> 08:34.640
You won't give in,

08:35.559 --> 08:37.000
even with the evidence right here.

08:37.679 --> 08:41.000
Ms. Yu's wounds
were clearly made by a demon's claws.

08:42.919 --> 08:45.880
That's because
the murder weapon you used is special.

08:45.960 --> 08:47.800
You're really clever.

08:48.680 --> 08:50.480
After you led us to the dye workshop,

08:50.560 --> 08:51.880
you went straight to Ms. Yu.

08:52.400 --> 08:53.360
A fox demon!

08:53.880 --> 08:55.120
It's at the dye workshop!

09:39.080 --> 09:40.040
Let's go!

09:42.160 --> 09:43.120
Go?

09:57.160 --> 09:58.960
I don't want to be left
with nothing again.

09:59.920 --> 10:01.520
I don't want to start over.

10:03.400 --> 10:05.360
I don't want to be homeless anymore.

10:06.760 --> 10:09.240
You kept making me…

10:10.040 --> 10:12.040
my favorite chestnut cake,

10:12.120 --> 10:15.120
just to make me happy, didn't you?

10:15.760 --> 10:16.800
And…

10:17.400 --> 10:19.840
you prepared cakes for me

10:20.640 --> 10:22.560
and put them in my bag…

10:27.080 --> 10:28.160
Actually,

10:28.800 --> 10:32.360
you wanted to come with me…

10:36.040 --> 10:37.560
What are you talking about?

10:44.560 --> 10:47.000
I never prepared
any chestnut cake for you.

10:48.880 --> 10:50.600
What I've been preparing

10:51.200 --> 10:53.120
is something else.

10:55.120 --> 10:56.320
All along,

10:58.440 --> 11:00.760
I've been copying Wei Qing's handwriting.

11:01.520 --> 11:05.160
Using his handwriting, I wrote a contract.

11:05.920 --> 11:07.480
Now that he's dead,

11:08.720 --> 11:10.160
if you die too,

11:10.880 --> 11:13.560
the entire Wei cloth business
will be mine.

12:11.080 --> 12:14.000
<i>Too bad you were so nervous,</i>

12:14.520 --> 12:16.400
<i>you forgot about the heated red candle.</i>

12:16.920 --> 12:20.960
<i>Even a light touch</i>
<i>would leave a mark on it.</i>

12:23.120 --> 12:26.160
Need me to match the fingerprints on it,
Steward Luo?

12:37.240 --> 12:38.680
-It was you!
-What?

12:38.760 --> 12:40.400
You killed Shengwei!

12:40.480 --> 12:41.920
You killed Shengwei!

12:52.200 --> 12:53.240
The waning moon mark!

12:55.000 --> 12:55.920
No.

12:56.440 --> 12:57.920
It's just a similar tattoo.

12:58.000 --> 12:59.880
I was born with this mark.

13:00.920 --> 13:02.760
We agreed to become sworn sisters, right?

13:03.760 --> 13:04.880
<i>Then I'll get one too.</i>

13:05.640 --> 13:07.600
You don't deserve it!

13:16.760 --> 13:18.560
I really don't.

13:21.680 --> 13:24.360
You're powerful demon hunters,

13:26.320 --> 13:28.520
wealthy nobles from prestigious families.

13:32.160 --> 13:34.600
Have you ever known hunger and cold,

13:35.400 --> 13:38.960
been bullied every day, and trampled upon?

13:44.040 --> 13:46.240
The Shilin Sect preaches
protecting the people,

13:46.320 --> 13:47.640
loving all living beings.

13:49.240 --> 13:50.320
Then let me ask you.

13:51.920 --> 13:55.920
Don't the folks in the old town count?

14:05.960 --> 14:08.080
The wailing there never stops.

14:08.160 --> 14:09.840
<i>You don't hear it?</i>

14:15.040 --> 14:15.880
‎I'm hungry.

14:23.040 --> 14:24.920
<i>But Ms. Yu never bullied you.</i>

14:25.440 --> 14:27.440
<i>She even pulled you from the pit.</i>

14:27.520 --> 14:29.360
No matter how bitter you feel,

14:29.880 --> 14:31.240
she doesn't deserve your hatred.

14:32.000 --> 14:35.640
I just don't want to be living
in fear again.

14:37.400 --> 14:40.280
I didn't want to give up
the wealth and comfort before me.

14:43.080 --> 14:44.360
Was that wrong?

14:48.840 --> 14:49.800
Yes.

14:53.560 --> 14:54.760
But I accept that.

14:58.400 --> 14:59.840
Those who've been rained on

15:00.360 --> 15:02.360
should be more willing
to lend an umbrella.

15:03.560 --> 15:04.560
However…

15:05.520 --> 15:08.680
you kept the umbrella for yourself
kindly lent to you.

15:09.560 --> 15:10.880
Even demons are grateful.

15:12.120 --> 15:13.160
You're worse than a demon.

15:15.520 --> 15:17.360
The world is cold and bleak.

15:19.440 --> 15:21.080
A caring heart is hard to find.

15:22.320 --> 15:25.080
I've been searching for that caring heart

15:25.160 --> 15:28.520
in the vast sea of people,
lifetime after lifetime.

15:28.600 --> 15:30.640
The pain is unbearable.

15:36.240 --> 15:37.160
But you…

15:38.880 --> 15:42.200
You killed the one
who truly cared for you.

15:54.440 --> 15:55.840
After hundreds of years,

15:58.960 --> 16:00.240
I still don't get

16:03.440 --> 16:05.720
the human heart.

16:21.440 --> 16:23.600
GIFT REGISTER

16:24.800 --> 16:25.800
What's this?

16:25.880 --> 16:28.280
The list Xiaowei put a death curse on.

16:29.760 --> 16:30.720
She gave it to me.

16:33.800 --> 16:34.800
GIFT REGISTER

16:44.760 --> 16:46.120
It's gone!

16:46.720 --> 16:47.600
Look!

16:52.280 --> 16:55.440
Look, it's gone! It vanished!

16:55.520 --> 16:56.360
Let me taste something.

17:01.200 --> 17:03.920
So fragrant! Here, great master,

17:04.440 --> 17:05.480
try some too.

17:10.400 --> 17:11.520
Right?

17:15.400 --> 17:16.359
What about Luo Wei?

17:16.960 --> 17:18.400
She's handed over to the authorities.

17:19.920 --> 17:21.040
And Xiaowei?

17:23.240 --> 17:24.480
People say

17:25.480 --> 17:28.240
scent is the longest-lasting memory.

17:31.160 --> 17:32.960
But I've already forgotten…

17:35.400 --> 17:36.920
<i>how long it's been</i>

17:38.560 --> 17:40.520
<i>since I last smelled flowers.</i>

18:02.480 --> 18:06.600
I will never smell flowers again.

18:17.800 --> 18:19.760
<i>I've smelled spring blooms</i>
<i>and autumn grass,</i>

18:20.640 --> 18:22.160
<i>rain, snow, wind, frost.</i>

18:23.440 --> 18:24.840
<i>I've smelled the world's delicacies,</i>

18:26.320 --> 18:27.880
the warm breath of daily life.

18:29.480 --> 18:31.040
That was when

18:33.640 --> 18:35.520
I felt most like a human.

18:37.040 --> 18:38.480
Too bad later,

18:39.440 --> 18:41.000
I couldn't smell anything anymore.

18:43.120 --> 18:46.640
I wanted to offer you
the very best of this world.

18:48.120 --> 18:49.520
I never imagined

18:49.600 --> 18:53.920
<i>a simple piece of chestnut cake</i>
<i>could make you so happy.</i>

18:55.000 --> 18:58.840
<i>Your joy was so simple,</i>
<i>yet I couldn't protect it.</i>

19:00.000 --> 19:01.200
For hundreds of years,

19:03.240 --> 19:04.920
lifetime after lifetime,

19:05.560 --> 19:07.240
I always wanted to keep you safe.

19:08.400 --> 19:09.600
But now,

19:10.640 --> 19:12.040
I've only harmed you.

19:33.600 --> 19:35.280
GOLDEN WEAVE

19:37.200 --> 19:38.560
Using magic again?

19:39.440 --> 19:40.400
Is he trying to get himeself killed?

20:26.400 --> 20:27.360
Wu…

20:31.600 --> 20:32.560
Lu…

20:42.440 --> 20:43.280
Wu…

20:49.680 --> 20:50.720
Lu…

20:53.640 --> 20:54.520
Lu…

21:20.920 --> 21:21.800
Thank you.

21:27.280 --> 21:28.800
The world is cold and bleak.

21:29.560 --> 21:30.680
A caring heart is hard to find.

21:31.200 --> 21:33.720
You can capture the form,
but never the heart.

21:36.320 --> 21:37.280
What a pity.

21:39.440 --> 21:40.960
You feel sorry for Xiaowei?

21:43.000 --> 21:45.000
Few hunters sympathize with demons.

21:46.760 --> 21:49.560
Under the sun, all beings suffer.

21:50.680 --> 21:52.400
When I see something heartbreaking,

21:53.240 --> 21:54.520
I feel sympathy.

21:55.360 --> 21:58.800
Demons can seduce hearts
but can hardly understand them.

22:00.560 --> 22:03.440
People always say
demons are cruel and cold-blooded,

22:03.960 --> 22:07.400
but they don't know
some are deeply obsessed with love.

22:08.840 --> 22:10.520
Yu Shengwei is just Yu Shengwei.

22:12.000 --> 22:13.680
She's no longer Wang Sheng.

22:14.480 --> 22:15.840
She doesn't know Xiaowei,

22:16.360 --> 22:18.000
never saved Xiaowei either.

22:18.600 --> 22:20.280
Xiaowei's deep affection

22:21.640 --> 22:23.160
is nothing but a pipe dream.

22:23.240 --> 22:25.960
Even exhausting a thousand years of magic,

22:26.040 --> 22:27.600
you can save the person,

22:29.280 --> 22:30.600
but not the heart.

22:31.720 --> 22:33.560
<i>He's trapped by his own obsession,</i>

22:34.240 --> 22:36.200
<i>mistaking gratitude for love.</i>

22:37.000 --> 22:38.920
<i>Few demons truly understand love.</i>

22:40.480 --> 22:41.800
With all that talk,

22:42.680 --> 22:44.800
you seem to know love pretty well.

22:46.360 --> 22:47.360
Of course.

22:48.480 --> 22:51.640
So, who loves you enough to die for you?

22:56.000 --> 22:57.200
Anyone?

23:02.240 --> 23:03.960
<i>Run, child!</i>

23:05.560 --> 23:07.440
You must survive!

23:22.840 --> 23:27.400
I never thought
someone would truly die for love.

23:28.200 --> 23:31.840
They say blood and tears are hot.

23:33.280 --> 23:34.880
Never thought one day

23:35.680 --> 23:37.960
I'd see tears turn to ice.

23:41.080 --> 23:44.240
Demons' tears are all fake,

23:46.040 --> 23:48.880
just to make themselves look more human.

23:50.520 --> 23:51.880
I really don't get it.

23:52.720 --> 23:53.880
Why are so many demons

23:54.640 --> 23:57.240
painting bones, painting skin,

23:58.600 --> 23:59.760
desperate to be human?

24:17.520 --> 24:18.560
Wangyan,

24:21.080 --> 24:23.280
are you sad for Xiaowei?

24:24.320 --> 24:26.600
I'm just recalling a lot of the past.

24:27.880 --> 24:29.560
<i>Since birth,</i>

24:29.640 --> 24:33.920
<i>our Nine-Tailed clan</i>
<i>have cultivated under the Fox Queen.</i>

24:34.000 --> 24:36.320
<i>She taught us like a mother,</i>

24:36.400 --> 24:41.280
<i>taking us along</i>
<i>to find colorful stones for Goddess Nuwa.</i>

24:41.960 --> 24:43.440
<i>After the Fox Queen passed,</i>

24:44.240 --> 24:47.040
<i>Goddess Nuwa channeled the moon's power,</i>

24:47.120 --> 24:50.280
<i>granting us, the Fox Queen's descendants,</i>
<i>the power of endless rebirth.</i>

24:51.040 --> 24:52.160
<i>From then on,</i>

24:52.240 --> 24:55.200
<i>we formed the Formless Moon Sect,</i>

24:56.200 --> 24:59.400
<i>guarding the Oracle Stone left by Nuwa.</i>

25:01.440 --> 25:03.640
I thought with immortality,

25:04.440 --> 25:07.160
<i>we sisters would never</i>
<i>suffer separation again.</i>

25:09.040 --> 25:11.000
<i>But Xiaowei still left.</i>

25:12.760 --> 25:14.720
<i>Reunited after a hundred years,</i>

25:14.800 --> 25:16.920
it just ends up like this.

25:18.040 --> 25:19.480
Xiaowei was so silly.

25:20.200 --> 25:21.680
Fleeing the sect,

25:22.720 --> 25:24.400
enduring the pain of losing her tail,

25:25.880 --> 25:30.480
and living in hiding
just to stay by one person.

25:31.600 --> 25:34.640
No magic for even the simplest things,

25:34.720 --> 25:36.560
<i>ending up with cuts and bruises.</i>

25:37.640 --> 25:40.160
Those chestnut cakes
were all made by Xiaowei's own hands.

25:40.920 --> 25:42.480
Just like an ordinary person,

25:42.560 --> 25:45.560
<i>Xiaowei sliced chestnuts piece by piece,</i>

25:45.640 --> 25:47.800
<i>mashing them into paste,</i>

25:47.880 --> 25:49.440
<i>and making cakes.</i>

25:50.600 --> 25:52.640
<i>Like cutting open its own heart,</i>

25:53.160 --> 25:54.880
<i>just to make the loved one happy.</i>

25:55.480 --> 25:57.560
And this is how it ended.

25:58.920 --> 26:00.640
Love in this world…

26:03.720 --> 26:04.880
Better off without it.

26:06.520 --> 26:07.560
Yeah.

26:08.440 --> 26:12.440
Love in this world really is complicated.

26:16.480 --> 26:18.400
Don't worry.

26:18.480 --> 26:21.720
I'll never betray you or our sect.

26:35.240 --> 26:38.360
Wangyan, you wouldn't either, right?

26:42.120 --> 26:45.120
I don't understand love, nor hate.

26:46.640 --> 26:48.160
I don't think I've ever loved anyone

26:48.920 --> 26:50.960
or hated anyone either.

26:52.400 --> 26:53.640
I guess

26:53.720 --> 26:55.360
-I'm just…
-A woodenhead.

26:57.520 --> 27:01.400
When a guy is clueless
and don't get romance,

27:02.160 --> 27:03.200
young girls call him a woodenhead.

27:04.920 --> 27:07.480
Fine, I'm a woodenhead then.

27:08.200 --> 27:09.280
No, you're not.

27:10.080 --> 27:11.560
I think Miss Lu Wuyi is more like one.

27:16.120 --> 27:17.160
Miss Lu?

27:18.440 --> 27:21.200
Miss Lu… is clever.

27:21.280 --> 27:22.960
Then she's pretending to be dumb.

27:23.800 --> 27:24.920
You like her so much.

27:25.000 --> 27:26.360
Even a woodenhead can see it.

27:35.640 --> 27:37.040
Is it that obvious?

27:39.480 --> 27:40.520
Oh man.

27:41.880 --> 27:44.760
Miss Wu said they're taking Xiaowei back.

27:44.840 --> 27:46.120
That won't do! Xiaowei still owes…

27:49.600 --> 27:52.200
Xiaowei is coming with us.

27:52.280 --> 27:54.200
Can you beat Lu Wuyi and Wu Wangyan?

27:55.960 --> 27:57.600
You and me

27:58.920 --> 28:00.880
are a match for them, right?

28:01.880 --> 28:03.000
It's just…

28:04.600 --> 28:06.080
I don't want to fight Miss Lu.

28:06.920 --> 28:07.960
In your dreams, you're a match.

28:09.440 --> 28:11.040
I'll help you bring Xiaowei
to the Shilin Sect.

28:13.640 --> 28:15.280
Why would you help?

28:15.920 --> 28:19.000
I was hunting Xiaowei
for the bounty anyway.

28:19.080 --> 28:22.080
Didn't they say,
catch the heart-ripping killer,

28:22.680 --> 28:24.560
and you get into the Shilin Sect?

28:26.040 --> 28:27.600
So you want to join the Shilin Sect?

28:27.680 --> 28:29.440
That's easy for me to arrange.

28:31.040 --> 28:33.880
So you have such a high status
in the Shilin Sect?

28:35.880 --> 28:37.000
His words?

28:37.520 --> 28:39.480
Half of it is trash.

28:39.560 --> 28:41.240
Count yourself lucky

28:41.320 --> 28:43.320
if you can scrape together
a couple of truths.

28:49.760 --> 28:52.000
But if you really can bring Xiaowei to us,

28:53.000 --> 28:54.280
getting into the sect
shouldn't be a problem.

28:57.160 --> 28:58.040
Give it back first.

28:59.680 --> 29:00.520
Give what?

29:01.320 --> 29:02.480
It's on you.

29:03.000 --> 29:04.240
I can smell it.

29:10.440 --> 29:12.280
You mean this Cosmic Pouch

29:12.360 --> 29:13.800
and the little demon within?

29:14.320 --> 29:16.000
No need to trouble you.

29:16.080 --> 29:18.080
We'll just take him back with us.

29:18.160 --> 29:21.000
If we find no evil deeds from him,

29:21.080 --> 29:23.160
we'll keep him as a pet.

29:24.760 --> 29:26.640
He's even biting through the bag?

29:29.800 --> 29:30.640
That's a dog.

29:34.920 --> 29:37.600
A demon hunter carrying a demon around?

29:38.200 --> 29:39.960
-Are you crazy?
-Nonsense!

29:40.040 --> 29:41.200
Young man,

29:41.280 --> 29:43.720
quit calling me a demon. It sounds awful.

29:43.800 --> 29:44.640
Me,

29:45.440 --> 29:47.720
I'm family with him, buddies with him.

29:47.800 --> 29:48.880
More like a follower.

29:50.760 --> 29:51.600
So…

29:51.680 --> 29:53.560
you're a weasel's follower?

29:55.080 --> 29:56.200
That's rough.

29:56.800 --> 29:58.280
No wonder you want to join our sect.

29:58.360 --> 29:59.400
Enough.

29:59.480 --> 30:00.360
Save him some face.

30:00.440 --> 30:01.760
He's my follower!

30:01.840 --> 30:03.560
I need a spy, an accomplice…

30:05.880 --> 30:07.080
Well, a helper.

30:07.160 --> 30:08.120
What's wrong with that?

30:08.800 --> 30:09.760
Nothing.

30:10.280 --> 30:13.320
True. After all,
weasels always live in packs,

30:13.400 --> 30:14.880
sneaking around everywhere,

30:14.960 --> 30:17.000
best at sniffing out gossip.

30:17.080 --> 30:18.120
Perfect for a spy.

30:18.800 --> 30:20.720
Li Jie, when we get back,

30:20.800 --> 30:23.280
let's get a captured weasel
to switch sides.

30:23.360 --> 30:24.360
Seems useful.

30:24.440 --> 30:25.960
I heard that!

30:26.960 --> 30:28.240
Both my ears heard it!

30:28.320 --> 30:29.880
Your ears are so small!

30:31.320 --> 30:32.440
Li Jie, look…

30:35.440 --> 30:36.680
His are even smaller.

30:40.880 --> 30:43.240
Little mouse.
You weasels all come in packs.

30:43.320 --> 30:44.240
You got names?

30:44.320 --> 30:46.040
How rude!

30:46.680 --> 30:47.640
Little mouse?

30:48.800 --> 30:52.440
Among humans,
we're called the Yellow Spirit.

30:52.520 --> 30:54.400
And we name ourselves carefully.

30:54.920 --> 30:56.800
Our elders use the first thing we steal

30:56.880 --> 30:58.320
to name us.

30:59.400 --> 31:03.400
And the first thing I ever got
was a ruler.

31:03.920 --> 31:05.120
Plus, we're weasels.

31:05.200 --> 31:06.160
So, you're "Ruler Weasel"?

31:07.160 --> 31:08.200
What's that thing?

31:09.520 --> 31:10.520
Ridiculous!

31:11.400 --> 31:13.320
Who'd have such a lousy name?

31:13.400 --> 31:14.240
My surname is You,

31:14.880 --> 31:16.040
and my given name is Chi.

31:16.680 --> 31:17.720
Catchy, right?

31:20.680 --> 31:21.840
Yeah…

31:22.360 --> 31:23.400
Very catchy.

31:34.280 --> 31:35.120
Miss Lu.

31:38.960 --> 31:40.040
Stop right there.

31:42.120 --> 31:43.080
Want to go in?

31:45.120 --> 31:46.120
No, you can't.

31:47.040 --> 31:48.760
Xiaowei is from our Formless Moon Sect.

31:48.840 --> 31:50.960
You can't take him.

31:52.520 --> 31:54.680
Ji, you're such a nice guy.

31:55.280 --> 31:56.760
Don't make me fight you, okay?

31:57.800 --> 31:58.640
You already fought.

32:00.200 --> 32:01.760
Check with its master
before hitting the dog.

32:02.280 --> 32:03.280
With just you?

32:03.960 --> 32:04.920
You've got it backwards.

32:05.520 --> 32:08.280
Two lousy hunters from the Shilin Sect,

32:09.280 --> 32:10.960
not a single flower on your foreheads,

32:11.040 --> 32:13.760
wanting to take someone from us?

32:13.840 --> 32:14.680
Or…

32:14.760 --> 32:17.720
do you have some other noble status?

32:23.640 --> 32:24.760
So rude.

32:25.720 --> 32:26.680
Watch this.

32:30.840 --> 32:33.720
Miss Lu, we're old acquaintances

32:34.480 --> 32:36.560
and have a little connection.

32:36.640 --> 32:38.080
Just do me a small favor.

32:38.160 --> 32:39.880
Let me talk to Xiaowei alone.

32:39.960 --> 32:41.280
Can you?

32:41.880 --> 32:43.520
You want to talk?

32:46.000 --> 32:47.600
What's in it for me?

32:50.760 --> 32:52.920
What do you want? Name it.

32:56.760 --> 32:58.680
That ugly doll you always carry.

32:59.400 --> 33:00.440
Give it to me.

33:00.520 --> 33:01.360
How about that?

33:02.000 --> 33:02.960
No. No way!

33:03.920 --> 33:05.400
What's ugly about it?

33:06.280 --> 33:07.200
Miss Lu,

33:07.760 --> 33:10.240
I'll give you anything else,
but not this doll.

33:10.320 --> 33:11.600
Pick something else.

33:12.560 --> 33:13.680
Is it that important?

33:16.280 --> 33:18.160
Someone important gave it to me.

33:21.280 --> 33:22.640
So, you have someone important?

33:24.920 --> 33:26.600
Then forget about seeing Xiaowei.

33:27.280 --> 33:28.120
I…

33:29.280 --> 33:30.120
Miss Lu…

33:32.080 --> 33:34.720
Alright, Wuyi. Stop teasing Mr. Ji.

33:35.960 --> 33:37.200
Mr. Ji,

33:37.280 --> 33:39.520
we did work together.

33:41.680 --> 33:44.120
You helped us catch Xiaowei.
I'll let you see him.

33:45.760 --> 33:49.800
But remember you owe us a big favor.

33:49.880 --> 33:51.000
No problem.

34:09.400 --> 34:10.679
You scared me!

34:17.239 --> 34:19.159
Scared you? You scared me!

34:21.000 --> 34:22.560
GOLDEN WEAVE

34:23.400 --> 34:25.679
Are you really helping Ji Ling
and that big guy

34:25.760 --> 34:27.560
take Xiaowei to their sect?

34:29.120 --> 34:30.000
What else?

34:30.080 --> 34:31.719
Take you instead?

34:32.560 --> 34:34.199
You're not worth the bounty.

34:36.360 --> 34:37.800
My pretty lady will get mad.

34:40.520 --> 34:41.400
Which pretty lady?

34:43.000 --> 34:44.679
Like seeing flowers in the mist,

34:45.760 --> 34:48.560
even through the pouch,
Miss Wu looks pretty.

34:51.040 --> 34:54.239
My head's full of Wu right now.

34:54.960 --> 34:57.280
Looks to me your head's misted.

34:58.400 --> 34:59.400
Is it?

35:00.280 --> 35:01.440
Don't forget our goal.

35:10.000 --> 35:10.920
A new demon?

35:22.320 --> 35:24.240
I know what you want to ask.

35:25.760 --> 35:27.840
Wangyan, you look upset.

35:27.920 --> 35:30.000
Something bothering you?

35:32.920 --> 35:35.840
So many people in Luo'an
asked for love talismans.

35:36.400 --> 35:40.160
All these hexed people
risk being cursed any time.

35:41.000 --> 35:43.880
You're worried how to fix it, right?

35:44.440 --> 35:46.400
You really know me best.

35:46.480 --> 35:48.000
It is strange.

35:48.520 --> 35:50.960
Xiaowei's been giving out talismans
for over ten years.

35:51.560 --> 35:54.920
Those hexed people lived normal lives.

35:55.440 --> 35:57.800
Why did they suddenly tear the talismans,

35:57.880 --> 35:59.000
getting their hearts ripped out?

35:59.760 --> 36:01.200
Someone must be behind this.

36:21.880 --> 36:24.440
So many people tearing talismans,
suffering the curse.

36:25.400 --> 36:28.200
Who's the mastermind behind all this?

36:31.480 --> 36:32.520
Speak!

36:43.920 --> 36:45.920
-Do you sense demonic energy?
-Of course.

36:46.520 --> 36:48.480
Xiaowei's using magic again.

36:49.080 --> 36:50.480
That crazy, reckless fool!

36:52.600 --> 36:53.560
No.

36:54.360 --> 36:55.880
Another demon is here.

37:03.760 --> 37:04.640
Rude.

37:08.160 --> 37:10.080
I let the Dragon Deity down.

37:10.840 --> 37:12.360
I broke my vow.

37:13.080 --> 37:16.720
Go back and tell him to be on guard.

37:17.600 --> 37:18.600
That person…

37:20.400 --> 37:21.520
is truly terrifying.

37:22.440 --> 37:23.280
Who?

37:24.440 --> 37:25.840
A butterfly demon.

37:27.160 --> 37:28.440
A month ago,

37:30.200 --> 37:31.800
he came to Weimiao Pavilion for me.

37:45.280 --> 37:47.160
<i>He said his name was Yuan Wuhuo,</i>

37:48.440 --> 37:50.360
<i>meaning "nothing gained".</i>

37:54.640 --> 37:56.280
Yuan Wuhuo…

38:07.680 --> 38:10.880
Sir, are you here for a love talisman?

38:11.800 --> 38:13.600
I'm here to grant your wish.

38:14.720 --> 38:16.000
Quite confident.

38:17.280 --> 38:19.240
You've been looking for someone,

38:19.320 --> 38:20.320
and I know where they are.

38:21.720 --> 38:24.520
Then tell me, who am I looking for?

38:26.040 --> 38:27.760
You're looking for Wang Sheng.

38:37.840 --> 38:40.920
Nothing in this world comes for free.

38:42.520 --> 38:43.800
What do you want?

38:43.880 --> 38:45.160
What a coincidence.

38:46.080 --> 38:48.920
My name is Yuan…

38:49.800 --> 38:50.800
Wuhuo.

38:51.560 --> 38:52.920
<i>He made two demands.</i>

38:53.720 --> 38:56.880
He wanted me to take back the nine-tailed
power I lent the Dragon Deity

38:57.480 --> 39:01.120
and to tell him how to reverse
the love talisman's spell.

39:02.920 --> 39:04.000
But he didn't lie to me.

39:05.000 --> 39:07.040
<i>He really helped me find Wang Sheng.</i>

39:23.800 --> 39:25.040
WEI MANSION

39:26.120 --> 39:27.280
What is that thing?

39:28.080 --> 39:30.040
How can it know everything?

39:35.160 --> 39:36.720
Heavenly Sticks.

39:38.680 --> 39:39.640
Heavenly Sticks?

39:41.080 --> 39:42.720
So this butterfly demon is something.

39:43.840 --> 39:45.000
Why?

39:45.080 --> 39:49.400
An immortal from thousands of years ago
left that magical tool.

39:49.480 --> 39:51.480
It can see fate and destiny.

39:51.560 --> 39:54.640
However, prying into fate comes at a cost.

39:54.720 --> 39:56.200
Each divination

39:56.720 --> 39:59.320
must be paid for with one's
own sacred power and lifespan.

40:01.240 --> 40:02.760
"Hard to come back.

40:05.800 --> 40:07.360
Hard to find again…"

40:13.120 --> 40:15.680
But the ancients said
fate cannot be revealed.

40:15.760 --> 40:18.560
So what the sticks can tell
is only an approximation.

40:19.760 --> 40:21.200
That's why I came to the Wei mansion,

40:21.280 --> 40:23.600
never expecting fate to toy with me.

40:24.960 --> 40:26.040
Perhaps…

40:26.560 --> 40:28.000
this is heaven's punishment for you.

40:29.360 --> 40:32.440
You made so many lovers part as strangers

40:32.520 --> 40:34.160
and the loveless wed as mates.

40:39.200 --> 40:42.960
I only helped those poor souls
like myself.

40:44.080 --> 40:45.560
Their love hurt too much.

40:46.360 --> 40:47.440
You're wrong,

40:48.160 --> 40:49.120
Xiaowei.

40:49.880 --> 40:52.800
After a thousand years of cultivation,
you still don't get it.

40:53.400 --> 40:54.560
Like people love flowers.

40:55.080 --> 40:57.560
In your hand, they're beautiful.

40:57.640 --> 41:00.640
On the branch, they're also beautiful.

41:01.520 --> 41:04.680
But those seeking talismans
are like picking flowers by force,

41:04.760 --> 41:08.640
only making them wither,
ending in tragedy.

41:10.800 --> 41:12.800
Yuan Wuhuo wanting you
to take back your magic,

41:12.880 --> 41:14.240
I can understand.

41:14.320 --> 41:17.160
But he lured
those hexed people to tear talismans,

41:17.880 --> 41:19.560
making them suffer the curse,

41:19.640 --> 41:21.120
why?

41:24.040 --> 41:25.280
I know his purpose.

41:26.000 --> 41:28.440
The Fox-Allure Spell in Luo'an
isn't lifted yet.

41:29.040 --> 41:31.200
So, you can't take Xiaowei.

41:32.440 --> 41:34.240
Her staying won't help.

41:34.320 --> 41:36.240
She can't even lift her own spell.

41:36.320 --> 41:40.040
Then we really can't
let a murderer walk away.

41:40.120 --> 41:41.560
Actually,

41:41.640 --> 41:43.800
I do know one power

41:43.880 --> 41:46.400
that can undo the spell's curse.

41:58.960 --> 42:00.000
Dragon Deity,

42:00.080 --> 42:01.720
please save us!
We're under the Fox-Allure Spell!

42:02.720 --> 42:05.520
-Please, Dragon Deity!
-Oh man, who spread the rumor

42:05.600 --> 42:08.840
that only the Dragon Deity's power
can undo the Fox-Allure Spell's curse?

42:08.920 --> 42:09.960
Who knows?

42:10.040 --> 42:11.680
Everyone with a love talisman

42:11.760 --> 42:14.480
gathered here, stuck kneeling.

42:16.360 --> 42:17.320
What a headache.

42:19.400 --> 42:20.600
The Dragon Deity's power?

42:24.960 --> 42:26.560
Can it really cleanse the spell?

42:27.080 --> 42:29.920
The Dragon Deity's power
can revive the dead,

42:30.000 --> 42:31.680
undo all spells and curses.

42:32.280 --> 42:33.640
However,

42:33.720 --> 42:36.040
I've heard some rumors lately.

42:36.120 --> 42:37.680
I don't know if they're true.

42:39.000 --> 42:40.440
You mean the rumor

42:40.520 --> 42:43.280
about the one worshiped by all,

42:43.360 --> 42:47.280
the last dragon son in the world, Chi Wen?

42:49.000 --> 42:50.120
What rumor?

42:51.200 --> 42:54.720
The rumor says Chi Wen…

42:54.800 --> 42:57.000
No longer has the Dragon Deity's power.

43:15.080 --> 43:16.040
Bai Ze.

43:17.960 --> 43:19.600
Master, you rarely summon me.

43:20.640 --> 43:21.640
What's it this time?

43:22.280 --> 43:23.720
After Xiaowei,

43:24.960 --> 43:28.920
Wu Zhiqi and Han Ba also broke their vows,

43:29.560 --> 43:32.120
taking back the power they lent me.

43:34.120 --> 43:37.040
In this Spirit-Binding Ring,
only your power remains.

43:37.720 --> 43:39.400
There must be a schemer

43:40.200 --> 43:42.440
behind their sudden betrayal.

43:42.520 --> 43:45.200
So I need you to find them.

43:45.280 --> 43:46.440
I know.

43:47.080 --> 43:48.760
I've already found Xiaowei.

43:49.440 --> 43:50.520
Right now,

43:50.600 --> 43:52.560
she's hiding in the Wei mansion in Luo'an.

43:53.240 --> 43:54.400
Master,

43:54.480 --> 43:56.280
you no longer have
the Dragon Deity's power.

43:56.360 --> 43:58.400
Please stay in the sect

43:59.160 --> 44:00.520
to be safe.

44:01.680 --> 44:06.760
So, now Chi Wen
can only stay in the Dragon Deity Temple,

44:06.840 --> 44:08.520
under the sect's tight protection.

44:08.600 --> 44:10.600
He occasionally receives petitioners

44:11.480 --> 44:14.320
but rarely ventures out,

44:14.840 --> 44:16.640
scared of being killed by demons.

44:18.080 --> 44:22.080
A dragon without its power
still counts as a deity?

44:23.320 --> 44:25.000
So pitiful.
